artifacts.summary: Phases 1-2 of plan v003 completed: omega^2 witness chain structure with 40 definitions/lemmas

partial_progress.details: Phase 2 (Inner Chain Properties) completed. Added 18 sorry-free lemmas including coverage_of_le (the key Phase 3 dependency). All compile via lake build. Remaining: Phase 3 (coverage argument/forward_F), Phase 4 (BFMCS integration), Phase 5 (backward_P).

completion_data.completion_summary: Completed Phase 2 of omega^2 witness chain properties for task 916. Proved 18 sorry-free lemmas including GContent/HContent multi-step monotonicity, F/P-formula dichotomy, G(neg)/H(neg) persistence and contrapositive, and the critical coverage_of_le lemma (if F(psi) alive at step n with encodeFormula(psi) <= n, then psi enters at encodeFormula(psi)+1). Phase 1 added 22 definitions/lemmas; combined total is 40 definitions/lemmas, all sorry-free. The 2 existing forward_F/backward_P sorries remain for Phase 3/5.
